## Dependency Management

### Adding New Dependencies

1. Consider bundle size impact
2. Check if native/browser API can achieve the same
3. Prefer small, focused packages over large frameworks
4. Document the reason for adding the dependency

### Blocked Dependencies

- Do NOT add Three.js (use Canvas 2D)
- Do NOT add large chart libraries (build custom viz)
- Do NOT add jQuery or similar DOM libraries
